        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2466.666666699999,
          "startTime": 8.6666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8633.333333300001,
          "startTime": 14.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、あの……すみません、読書中でしたか\n……あの。一体、何を読んでらっしゃるんですか？",
      "startTime": 15.672312228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "世界を股にかける、超一流スナイパーの漫画です\n凄く有名な作品ですよ、知らないんですか？",
      "startTime": 25.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ、事務所でくつろぐのは構わないんですが\n一応仕事場なので、漫画は退社後にお願いしますね……",
      "startTime": 32.5679582914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "失礼ですね。これも仕事の一環です",
      "startTime": 37.4508383752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、私、誕生日企画で漫画描いたじゃないですか\nあれから仕事先で漫画のこと聞かれる機会が増えまして",
      "startTime": 45.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "なのでこうして、話題作や名作に目を通して\n日頃から情報収集している訳です",
      "startTime": 53.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言われれば、仕事と言えなくもないですね",
      "startTime": 56.7856678169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんも以前、漫画原作の映画に出てから\n漫画ファン向けの企画に呼ばれたりもしてますし",
      "startTime": 64.4963950793,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}